query: SELECT MIN(cn1.name) AS first_company, MIN(cn2.name) AS second_company, MIN(mi_idx1.info) AS first_rating, MIN(mi_idx2.info) AS second_rating, MIN(t1.title) AS first_movie, MIN(t2.title) AS second_movie FROM company_name AS cn1, company_name AS cn2, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, kind_type AS kt1, kind_type AS kt2, link_type AS lt, movie_companies AS mc1, movie_companies AS mc2, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx1, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx2, movie_link AS ml, title AS t1, title AS t2 WHERE lt.id = ml.link_type_id AND t1.id = ml.movie_id AND t2.id = ml.linked_movie_id AND it1.id = mi_idx1.info_type_id AND t1.id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND kt1.id = t1.kind_id AND cn1.id = mc1.company_id AND t1.id = mc1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mi_idx1.movie_id AND ml.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND mi_idx1.movie_id = mc1.movie_id AND it2.id = mi_idx2.info_type_id AND t2.id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND kt2.id = t2.kind_id AND cn2.id = mc2.company_id AND t2.id = mc2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mi_idx2.movie_id AND ml.linked_movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND mi_idx2.movie_id = mc2.movie_id AND t2.production_year < 2009 AND (t2.title like '%night%' OR t2.title like '%battle%' OR t2.title like '%ship%' OR t2.title like '%hammer%') AND mi_idx2.info > '10.0' AND kt1.kind in ('video game','movie','tv series','episode','video movie','tv mini series') AND t1.production_year > 1998 AND t1.title not like '%star%' AND t1.title not like '%picture%' AND t1.title not like '%mystery%' AND it2.info in ('rentals','mini biography','salary history','gross','LD additional information','LD sound encoding','taglines','death date','biographical movies','locations','certificates','LD color rendition','LD production country','LD digital sound','death notes') AND (mc1.note like '%Italy%' OR mc1.note like '%Germany%' OR mc1.note like '%Mexico%') AND (mc2.note like '%Sweden%') AND lt.link in ('referenced in','followed by','spin off','references','featured in','edited from','remake of','follows','spoofs','version of','unknown link','spoofed in','edited into','alternate language version of','spin off from','similar to','remade as') AND cn2.country_code not in ('tm','kw','mz','br','am') AND kt2.kind in ('tv mini series','video game','episode','video movie','tv movie')
